data.description: Lovely, renovated 3bed/2 bath home in a desirable area in Paterson. The main level features open floor plan with Kitchen Living and Dining room which has sliders to the deck. 2nd floor has nice sized bedrooms and full bath, The basement is finished with a full bath and laundry room. Home has spacious yard with plenty of parking. Drive way is shared.
